5. **T5: Clip interaction handlers** -- Hit-testing, grid snapping (1/4, 1/8, 1/16, 1-bar), drag-move, trim, split, rubber-band selection
6. **T6: Session persistence** -- Typed SessionSchema with track/clip round-trip serialization

